This code implements `power()` with complexity **O(log(n))**:

    def power(x, y): 
        if y==0: 
            return 1
        n = power(x, y // 2)  
        if y % 2 == 0: 
            return n * n 
        else: 
            if y &gt; 0: 
                return x * n * n 
            else: 
                return (n * n) / x

